Third Depabtment,

September, 1947.

(September 10, 1947.) In the Matter of the Claim of Eric Stratton, Appellant, against Broadway Ignition Co. et al., Respondents. Workmen’s Compensation Board, Respondent.

Application for an order requiring appellant to be furnished with copy of record. Application denied. Motion to dismiss appeal granted. All concur.
